content: bucurdavid: Opened a significant PR #2327 for a Metaplex Bubblegum plugin, which involved extensive code changes across 2061 files (+143,884/-48,974 lines). Reported issue #2963 regarding build failures in the latest release version, which was subsequently closed. Activity was limited to just 2 days this month, with contributions primarily focused on code (47%) and configuration files (27%).
